Maintainer: Robert Burger <robert.burger@dlr.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Section: libs
Homepage: https://www.burger-system.de/robotkernel/service_provider_key_value
