Vcs-Git: https://github.com/robotkernel-hal/service_provider_key_value.git
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: service-provider-key-value-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: robotkernel-dev, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Robotkernel service provider to export key-value dictionary access services.
  This service provider gains unified access to key-value dictionaries of robotkernel
  modules. It support dictionary listing, reading and writing key-value pairs.

